parameters.name: DiagnosticKey
parameters.description:
The keyword in the diagnosis.

You can specify the ID of the stack that you want to diagnose.

parameters.name: DiagnosticType
parameters.description: The type of the item that is diagnosed. Set the value to Stack, which specifies that the stack is diagnosed.

parameters.name: Lang
parameters.description:
The language of the diagnostic report to be generated. Only Chinese and English are supported.

Valid values:

*   zh-cn
*   en

parameters.name: Product
parameters.description: The name of the product that is diagonosed.
